OL,6,FAlthough the safety issues raised were
OL,7,Fnot found to have caused Mr Ineson's
OL,8,Fdeath, Mr Place said there was a risk
OL,9,Fof further fatalities unless changes
OL,10,Fwere made.
OL,12,FHe wrote: "The evidence highlighted
OL,13,Funcertainty and confusion with regard
OL,14,Fto responsibility for aspects of
OL,15,Fsafety measures.
