OL,6,F"Some participants did not receive a
OL,7,Fsafety briefing, there was a lack of
OL,8,Fknowledge about the competency of
OL,9,Fswimmers, and no understanding of how
OL,10,Fmany people were in the water at any
OL,11,Fone time.
OL,13,F"It became clear in evidence that the
OL,14,Factivity does not require a licence
OL,15,Ffrom the Adventure Activities
OL,16,FLicensing Authority and can be
OL,17,Fundertaken and/or organised by anyone
OL,18,Fwithout regulation."
