OL,3,CCoroner urges government to act after
OL,4,Cman drowns at open water swimming event
OL,6,FThe report also noted an absence of
OL,7,Fformal requirements around risk
OL,8,Fassessments, emergency plans, sign-in/
OL,9,Fout procedures, and organiser training.
OL,11,FMr Place sent the warning ` known as a
OL,12,FRegulation 28 report ` to the
OL,13,FSecretary of State for Culture, Media
OL,14,Fand Sport and to the chief executive
OL,15,Fof the Health and Safety Executive.
OL,17,FThey have until 5 June 2025 to
OL,18,Frespond, setting out what action they
OL,19,Fpropose to take or explaining why none
OL,20,Fis planned.
